        "body": "Key Features Implemented:\r\n\r\n1. Homepage:\r\n- Developed the Home page displaying a list of movies\r\n- Implemented search functionality for filtering movies dynamically\r\n- Integrated reusable MovieCard components for displaying movie details\r\n\r\n2. Movie Details Page:\r\n- Created Movie Details page with complete information about selected movies\r\n- Displayed movie metadata such as title, rating, genre, duration, and description\r\n- Implemented show timings selection feature\r\n\r\n3. Booking History:\r\n- Implemented Booking History page to display previously booked tickets\r\n- Stored booking data locally to simulate real-world behavior\r\n- Displayed structured booking information for better user experience\r\n\r\n4. Data Integration:\r\n- Created and managed movie data using a centralized data file\r\n- Ensured dynamic rendering of content across different components\r\n\r\n5. User Flow Completion:\r\n- Completed full flow: Home → Movie Details → Seat Selection → Booking → History\r\n- Ensured smooth navigation and data consistency across pages.",
